                    <div id="wrap">
                        <section class="pt50 pb50">
                            <div class="container">
                                <h3 class="hr_title_horizontal mb30">Strategy</h3>
                                <div class="faq-list">
                                    <div class="faq d-flex mb30 align-items-end">
                                        <div>
                                            <h5 class="faq-title mb10">Establish a high-level communications
                                                infrastructure
                                            </h5>
                                            <p>The experiences gained at the international level have shown the
                                                necessity to provide a high-level infrastructure for communications and
                                                information technology for the development of various economic
                                                activities
                                                In modern societies, it is no secret that adopting the principle of
                                                competitiveness guarantees the continuity of the infrastructure and the
                                                continuous improvement of services to meet the needs of individuals and
                                                companies. And in
                                                In this regard, the Ministry looks forward to the future with its
                                                efforts to focus on providing the latest technologies in order to
                                                support economic and social development of all kinds.
                                                Their levels
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="faq d-flex mb30 align-items-end">
                                        <div>
                                            <h5 class="faq-title mb10">Post sector reform</h5>
                                            <p>The Libyan government realizes that a strong, world-class postal service
                                                operating within a competitive postal market can act as a valuable tool
                                                in achieving development goals.
                                                National, as effective postal services can reduce the value of financial
                                                and other corporate transactions, which means enhancing the principle of
                                                competitiveness at the national level
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="faq d-flex mb30 align-items-end">
                                        <div>
                                            <h5 class="faq-title mb10">Upgrading the regulatory framework for
                                                communication networks
                                            </h5>
                                            <p>Libya recognizes the importance of integration with the International
                                                Telecommunication and Information Technology Framework as a means to
                                                achieve its desired goals in the Libyan ICT sector
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                        <div class="oe_structure"/>
                    </div>
                </t>
            </t>
        </field>
